    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/0b805cae7cc2df7cd7f24657a0206b47.poster.avif?t=1761587566\" width=670 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/0b805cae7cc2df7cd7f24657a0206b47.webm?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店模拟器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/9976877bb9f4eb7d909f916fd5e1d0a1.poster.avif?t=1761587566\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/9976877bb9f4eb7d909f916fd5e1d0a1.webm?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/9976877bb9f4eb7d909f916fd5e1d0a1.mp4?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你现在拥有了自己的商店。这里有一些小建议：摆放货架时，确保它们之间有足够的空间。把昂贵的商品放在更显眼的位置。别忘了设置自动售货机。换上更好看的墙纸和地板。记得对顾客说谢谢。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >农场/生产模拟器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/62587b6059733b514254bc2da932a1bb.poster.avif?t=1761587566\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/62587b6059733b514254bc2da932a1bb.webm?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/62587b6059733b514254bc2da932a1bb.mp4?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >苹果汁和葡萄汁很棒，但苹果酒和葡萄酒更棒。你有一个农场和一家商店（多亏了你的奶奶）。收集农场资源，设置机器，生产酒精、香烟，或许还有其他东西。在你的商店里出售这些商品。这将会非常棒。奶奶会为此感到欣慰的。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >趣味故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/b1ccd75df2ee244794180ef2e6e60669.poster.avif?t=1761587566\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/b1ccd75df2ee244794180ef2e6e60669.webm?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189790/extras/b1ccd75df2ee244794180ef2e6e60669.mp4?t=1761587566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与邻居保持良好的关系很重要。很高兴你的邻居现在是如此美好的“人”——或者说，动物。别忘了和他们打招呼，他们会向你讲述他们的生活故事作为回报。</p>",
